<section id="services" class="bg-gray-100 border-b py-8">
    <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto m-8">
        <h2 class="w-full my-2 text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight text-center text-gray-800 mb-2">
            My Services
        </h2>
        <div class="w-full my-2 text-2xl md:text-3xl px-6 leading-tight text-center text-gray-600 mb-12">
            Affordable web, mobile, and OTT app development. <br />Get started today with a free virtual consultation.
        </div>

         <div id="pwa" class="md:mt-6">
            <Service IllustrationOnRight="@true">
                <Header>
                    SaaS Web Applications
                </Header>
                <Body>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Custom SaaS application development at a fraction of the cost. Software as a Service, also known as SaaS, stands for a cloud-based solution that can be used via mobile apps or browsers. The SaaS platform development is a software creation and launching model in which product is released via the subscription plan and is centrally hosted.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        SaaS is an approach to accessing applications on the Internet. In contrast with the traditional model, the apps are placed in remote cloud storage via the web or an API. SaaS applications are also known as web-based software, on-demand software, or hosted software.
                    </p>
                       <p class="mb-4 flex flex-col">
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Clean Architecture (for maintainability)</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Multi-tenant Architecture (ensures data is siloed)</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Authentication &amp; Authorization</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Microsoft's .NET Stack</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Microsoft's Azure Cloud Serivces</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Custom API</div>
                    </p>
                    <p class="my-4">
                        Examples of SaaS Applications: Monday.com, Canva, Slack, DocuSign, Salesforce, Squibler, G Suite, HubSpot
                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Contact me today and launch your own SaaS Web Application in 2023!.
                    </p>
                </Body>
                <SVGCode>
                    <PWADevSVG />
                </SVGCode>
            </Service>
        </div>



        <div id="ott" class="md:mt-6">
            <Service IllustrationOnRight="@false">
                <Header>
                    OTT Channels (Roku, Fire TV, Android TV, etc.)
                </Header>
                <Body>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        If you have a video streaming business, you can quickly increase your audience and revenue 20% - 30% with OTT apps.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        OTT (Over-the-Top) apps are apps that deliver video content over the internet instead of cable or satellite. They allow your customers to stream videos to mobile apps (iPhone and Android) and TVs using OTT streaming platforms like Roku, Fire TV, Android TV, and Apple TV. Choose from a variety of monetization options like ads supported video on demand (AVOD), subscription video on demand (SVOD), and transactional video on demand (TVOD), also known as pay-per-view.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4 flex flex-col">
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Drive sales &amp; subscriptions</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Build co-promotions marketing</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Expand visibility &amp; awareness</div>
                        <div><i class="fa fa-play text-primary mr-2"></i> Brand endorsements/partnerships</div>
                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Contact me today and launch your own OTT platform in 2023!.
                    </p>
                </Body>
                <SVGCode>
                    <OTTDevSVG />
                </SVGCode>
            </Service>
        </div>




