        <div id="mobile" class="md:mt-6">
            <Service IllustrationOnRight="@true">
                <Header>
                    Mobile Apps (Android/iPhone)
                </Header>
                <Body>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        My goal is to build Android/iPhone apps that give your app users the best experience possible. I'll utilize the lastest UX (user experience) theory to make sure your app users love your app.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        And I'll leverage “cross-platform” capabilities, which saves me development time and therefore saves you money.
