                </Header>
                <Body>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        An estimated 35% of the gazillion websites on the web were built using WordPress (what is 35% of a gazillion?). WordPress is used to build virtually any type of website &mdash; eCommerce, blogs, promotional, content management system, religious, online communities, niche affiliate websites, online courses and many more.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Hiring a web design agency can cost anywhere from $5,000 to $50,000, depending on the features you require.
                        This is fine for big companies with fat bank accounts.
                        But for smaller companies, organizations, and individuals that are working with a tight budget, WordPress development might be the better choice.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Contact me today and tell me about the website you want. I'll be glad to help you decide if WordPress is the right choice for you.
